Set Shell "bash"
Set Width 1200
Set Height 600
Set FontSize 14
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set Padding 10
Set TypingSpeed 0

Type "./target/release/smartgameviewer examples/AlphaGo_LeeSedol_game4.sgf"
Enter
Sleep 2s
Space
Sleep 200ms
Right 50
Sleep 200ms
Right 50
Sleep 200ms
Right 20
Sleep 500ms
Screenshot images/midgame.png
Type "q"
Sleep 500ms
